OL,3,CFire services across Wales under
OL,4,Cpressure due to rise in wildfires
OL,6,FFire services across Wales say they
OL,7,Fare under pressure following a series
OL,8,Fof wildfires across Wales in the last
OL,9,Ffew weeks.
OL,11,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,12,Fhas responded to 390 wildfires since
OL,13,FJanuary this year. This is
OL,14,Fsubstantially more than January to
OL,15,FApril in 2024, where there were 33
OL,16,Fwildfires.
OL,18,FNorth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,19,Fhas responded to 40 more wildfires
OL,20,Fthis year than it did in the first 4
OL,21,Fmonths of 2024.
