OL,3,CFire services across Wales under
OL,4,Cpressure due to rise in wildfires
OL,6,FIn the last week alone, Mid and West
OL,7,FWales Fire and Rescue Service has
OL,8,Fattended 192 grass fires. Thirteen of
OL,9,Fthese fires have been over 10 hectares
OL,10,Fin size.
OL,12,FWith the increase amount of fires, the
OL,13,Ffire service have receive an influx of
OL,14,Fcalls.
OL,16,FMid and West Wales Joint Fire Control
OL,17,FCentre operators dealt with over 1,000
OL,18,Fcalls during one 24-hour period.
