OL,3,CFire services across Wales under
OL,4,Cpressure due to rise in wildfires
OL,6,FSouth Wales Fire and Rescue Service
OL,7,Fhas urged the public to 'dial 999 if
OL,8,Ftheir lives or property are in
OL,9,Fdanger'. It also reminded the public
OL,10,Fto check their social media account to
OL,11,Fsee if they are already dealing with
OL,12,Fwildfire before calling to report it.
OL,14,FCFO Roger Thomas KFSM has commended
OL,15,Fthe resilience, teamwork and
OL,16,Fcommitment that the Service's
OL,17,Foperational crew members and Joint
OL,18,FFire Control (JFC) Centre operators
OL,19,Fhave demonstrated during challenging
OL,20,Fconditions.
