OL,3,CFire services across Wales under
OL,4,Cpressure due to rise in wildfires
OL,6,F"The recent surge in the number of
OL,7,Fgrass fires has put immense pressure
OL,8,Fon our resources, yet our staff have
OL,9,Fall demonstrated the professionalism,
OL,10,Fresilience and teamwork that define
OL,11,Four Service. Our staff have also shown
OL,12,Ftheir continued commitment to
OL,13,Fprotecting the communities we serve.
OL,15,FTheir tireless efforts, often in
OL,16,Fextreme and challenging conditions,
OL,17,Fhave not gone unnoticed by myself, the
OL,18,FExecutive Leadership Team and Members
OL,19,Fof our Fire Authority."
